title: Endgame
body:
Okay I guess you survived... 
Dr. Green had to die for you to move on. 
He was holding us back, trying to call all the shots in MY level...
Above me is the Game Key that will grant you access the next level called "Mother Nature" 
Even though it should be called "Mother B*tch" because of that nasty Dryad...
In case you are as bright as you look the Game Key is "Horror3". 
The Game Key will also let you go to a bonus game called "The House that Haunts Us"  
I call it the Wh*re House because of that pervert Jack, but anyways
Click me if you need to see all that again... Click me nicely... or I'll find you later...
